reviewText: One of the best movies of Ai Shinozaki
NO IT DIDN'T MEET MY EXPECTATIONS. I WAS EXPECTING MORE.
Cute little movie.  It's not great but is a fun "teen romantic adventure" (which is the best metopher I can use).  It's fun for a movie night at home.
This is one of my favorite actresses. I highly recommend this movie for anyone who is a fan of this genre...
